law.catch_line: KRS 136.060 and 136.070 not applicable to membership certificates, stock, or other evidence of member, shareholder or patron interest.
law.text: The provisions of KRS 136.060 and 136.070 shall not apply to the issuance of membership certificates, shares of stock or any other evidence of member, shareholder, or patron interest by any such agricultural cooperative association.
law.history: Amended 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 12, sec. 1, effective March 1, 1976. -- Created 1968 Ky. Acts ch. 148, sec. 7.
